des:
Introducing the Kettal Kode – Your voice-controlled Fan companion! With this skill, you can effortlessly control your Kettal Superfan using just your voice commands. Adjust the fan speed, and create the perfect indoor/outdoor climate without lifting a finger. Say goodbye to the hassle of remote controls and embrace the future of smart, hands-free cooling with Kettal Superfan!

The following is a step by step guide:
1. Download our "Kettal Kode" app in app market, then register an account (or log in directly if you already have an account);
2. Configure our devices in "Kettal Kode" app and change appropriate name for your devices;
3. Enable "Kettal Kode" skill on Alexa app, you'll be navigated to the login page, follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
4. Tell Echo "Alexa, discover my devices". Wait for Echo to say "Search complete";
5. Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
Alexa, turn on the fan.
Alexa, turn off the fan.
Alexa, set the fan speed to 1.
